'''唇萼薄荷'''（[[学名|学名]]：''{{lang|la|Mentha pulegium}}''），又称'''普列薄荷'''（{{lang|en|Pennyroyal}}）、'''除蚤薄荷'''、'''胡薄荷'''，为[[薄荷属|薄荷属]]下的一个[[种|种]]。碾碎的唇萼薄荷会有类似[[绿薄荷|绿薄荷]]的浓香气味。它也是一种传统的[[调料|烹饪调料]]、[[草药|草药]]和[[堕胎药|堕胎药]]。

== 使用历史 ==
唇萼薄荷曾被[[古希腊|古希腊]]和[[古罗马|古罗马]]人当作烹饪调料。古希腊人通常把其作为酒的添加材料，而它也是古罗马美食食谱的常客，并与[[独活草|独活草]]、[[牛至|牛至]]和[[香菜|香菜]]一并使用。尽管在中世纪它的使用非常广泛，现在渐渐已经不再受到烹饪师的青睐了。

而作为一个简易的毒物，唇萼薄荷的使用却有悠久的历史。早期的殖民者利用烘干的唇萼薄荷祛除害虫。它如此受欢迎，以至于[[英国皇家学会|英国皇家学会]]在第一版的《[[哲学会刊|哲学会刊]]》（{{lang|en|Philosophical Transactions}}，1665年）都刊登了一篇论文用它的毒性与[[响尾蛇|响尾蛇]]作比较<ref>Royal Society, "Of A Way of Killing Ratle-Snakes," Philosophical Transactions Vol. 1 (1665) p. 43.</ref>。

==毒性==
唇萼薄荷的香精油极其集中。因为其烈毒性，它不能被内服：哪怕是很小的剂量，都可能致死。尝试使用它作为[[避孕药|避孕药]]的[[并发症|并发症]]已经被报道。该精油液可以用作[[芳香疗法|芳香疗法]]，一种洗浴的添加料和[[杀虫剂|杀虫剂]]。但已经有大量研究显示，这种薄荷对人类和动物具有很强毒性<ref name="Ann Intern Med">{{cite journal |last=Anderson |first=Ilene B. |coauthors=Sidney D. Nelson and Paul D. Blanc |date=1 February 1997 |title=Pennyroyal Metabolites in Human Poisoning |journal=[[Annals_of_Internal_Medicine|Annals of Internal Medicine]] |volume=126 |issue=3 |pages=250–251 |url=http://www.annals.org/cgi/content/full/126/3/250-a |accessdate=2008-06-25 |pmid=9027280 |archive-date=2009-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090214134409/http://www.annals.org/cgi/content/full/126/3/250-a |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Ann Intern Med 2">{{cite journal |last=Anderson |first=Ilene B. |coauthors=Walter H. Mullen; James E. Meeker; Siamak C. Khojasteh-Bakht; Shimako Oishi; Sidney D. Nelson; and Paul D. Blanc |date=15 April 1996 |title=Pennyroyal Toxicity: Measurement of Toxic Metabolite Levels in Two Cases and Review of the Literature |journal=[[Annals_of_Internal_Medicine|Annals of Internal Medicine]] |volume=124 |issue=8 |pages=726–734 |url=http://www.annals.org/cgi/content/full/124/8/726 |accessdate=2008-06-25 |pmid=8633832 |archive-date=2009-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090809234310/http://www.annals.org/cgi/content/full/124/8/726 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Pediatrics">{{cite journal |last=Bakerink |first=James A. |coauthors=Sidney M. Gospe Jr; Robert J. Dimand; and Marlowe W. Eldridge |date=1 November 1996 |title=Multiple Organ Failure After Ingestion of Pennyroyal Oil From Herbal Tea in Two Infants |journal=[[Pediatrics_(journal)|Pediatrics]] |volume=98 |issue=5 |pages=944–947 |url=http://pediatrics.aappublications.org/cgi/content/abstract/98/5/944 |accessdate=2008-06-25 |pmid=8909490 |archive-date=2009-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090214100413/http://pediatrics.aappublications.org/cgi/content/abstract/98/5/944 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="JAVMA">{{cite journal |last=Sudekum |first=M |coauthors=Poppenga, R H; Raju, N; Braselton, W E Jr. |title=Pennyroyal oil toxicosis in a dog |journal=Journal of the American Veterinary Medical Association |volume=200 |issue=6 |pages=817–818 |pmid=1568929 |url= |accessdate=|date=March 1992}}</ref>，甚至是极小的程度都具有危险<ref>{{cite web |url=http://bitsandbrew.com/warning1.htm |title=Warnings about Essential Oils |accessdate=2008-06-25 |publisher=Bits and Brew |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080423092220/http://bitsandbrew.com/warning1.htm |archivedate=2008-04-23 }}</ref>。

直到1994年，[[美国国会|美国国会]]通过了《膳食补充剂健康教育法》（{{lang|en|Dietary Supplement Health and Education Act}}），所有的唇萼薄荷产品才被标示警告“孕妇禁用”<ref name="medline">{{cite web |url=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/druginfo/natural/patient-pennyroyal.html |title=American pennyroyal (Hedeoma pulegioides L.), European pennyroyal (Mentha pulegium L.) |accessdate=2008-06-25 |date=2008-02-01 |author=Natural Standard Research Collaboration |publisher=Natural Standard |archive-date=2010-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100718133101/http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/druginfo/natural/patient-pennyroyal.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 文学作品 ==
[[阿里斯托芬|阿里斯托芬]]在《[[利西翠妲|利西翠妲]]》和《和平》的著作中已经提及唇萼薄荷作为[[堕胎药|堕胎药]]的历史。

